(Zippy_stat: Zippy  ↔  Bob)
(Alice_stat: Alice  ↔  (¬ Zippy ∨ Zoey))
(Zoey_stat: Zoey  ↔ Joe)
:(Alice ∧ ¬Ted)
:= by
```

